TABLE.name: Main Information Table for NED objects within 1.000 arcmin of object MESSIER 001
TABLE.DESCRIPTION: Main information about object (Cone Search results)

FIELD.name: No.
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: A sequential object number applicable to this list only.

FIELD.name: Object Name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: NED preferred name for the object

FIELD.name: Velocity
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Velocity in km/sec, based on known heliocentric redshift

FIELD.name: Redshift
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Heliocentric redshift for the object, if it exists in NED

FIELD.name: Redshift Flag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Quality flag for known heliocentric redshift

FIELD.name: Magnitude and Filter
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: NED's Basic Data magnitude and filter, generally in an optical band.

FIELD.name: Distance (arcmin)
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Distance of the source from the queried position (arcmin);listed as blank if not applicable.

FIELD.name: References
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of literature references in NED

FIELD.name: Notes
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of catalog notes in NED

FIELD.name: Photometry Points
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of photometric data points stored by NED for the object

FIELD.name: Positions
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of position data points stored by NED for the object

FIELD.name: Redshift Points
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of redshift data points stored by NED for the object.

FIELD.name: Diameter Points
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of diameter data points stored by NED for the object.

FIELD.name: Associations
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of NED associations for the object.
